14.1.1. Traccar Integration (HLD Notes)

Notes from the HLD: 

  


This software needs to integrate with Traccar.

  


The OBD-II device will likely be the Freematics ONE+ Traccar Edition.

  


User accounts will need to sync:

  * Name
  * Email
  * Phone
  * Disabled
  * Speed Unit - mph
  * Distance Unit - mi
  * Altitude Unit - ft
  * Volume Unit - U.S. Gallon
  * Time Zone - requires translation



  


New Devices must be sent to Traccar with:

  * Name
  * Identifier



  


The software will need to import:

  * Positions
  * Events
  * Trips
